OL,3,CPregnant women urged to vaccinate as
OL,4,Cthree more babies die from whooping
OL,5,Ccough
OL,7,FThree infants died from whooping cough
OL,8,Fin the UK during April, new data from
OL,9,Fthe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,10,Fhas shown.
OL,12,FThe latest data brings the total to
OL,13,Feight deaths from the illness in 2024
OL,14,Fso far.
OL,16,FPregnant women are being urged to take
OL,17,Fup the offer of the so they can pass
OL,18,Fon protection to their babies, which
OL,19,Fshould last until they are old enough
OL,20,Fto get vaccinated themselves.
