OL,7,FThe UK is experiencing a rapid rise in
OL,8,F, with almost 5,000 cases confirmed
OL,9,Fbetween January and April 2024.
OL,11,FThe new figures released on Thursday
OL,12,Fshow there were 1,888 confirmed cases
OL,13,Fof the illness in April 2024.
OL,15,FThat's up from 1,319 cases in March,
OL,16,F918 in February and 556 in January.
OL,18,FAll together since January there have
OL,19,Fbeen 4,793 confirmed cases of whooping
OL,20,Fcough this year.
