OL,7,FThis compares to just 858 cases of
OL,8,Fwhooping cough for the whole of 2023.
OL,10,FThe leap in cases between March and
OL,11,FApril 2024 was the largest rise yet,
OL,12,Fwith 569 more cases detected.
OL,14,FThe bacterial infection, also known as
OL,15,Fpertussis, affects the lungs and
OL,16,Fbreathing tubes. Also called the "100
OL,17,Fday cough" because of the long
OL,18,Frecovery time, the illness spreads
OL,19,Fvery easily.
