OL,7,FBetween January and the end of April,
OL,8,Fsomewere diagnosed with whooping cough.
OL,10,FAround half of the latest cases have
OL,11,Fbeen recorded in people aged 15 years
OL,12,For older and 26% among children aged
OL,13,Fbetween 10 and 14 years.
