OL,7,FWhen babies are eight weeks old, they
OL,8,Fare able to have the six-in-one
OL,9,Fvaccine which includes immunisation
OL,10,Fagainst whooping cough.
OL,12,FUKHSA said the are similar to a cold,
OL,13,Fsuch as a runny nose and sore throat,
OL,14,Fbut the infection can develop into
OL,15,Fcoughing bouts that last for a few
OL,16,Fminutes and are typically worse at
OL,17,Fnight.
